      <title>埃塞俄比亚赢得融资保证是获得新 IMF 贷款的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ethiopia-wins-financing-assurances-key-to-unlock-new-imf-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，埃塞俄比亚官方债权人已向该国提供融资保证，以帮助国际货币基金组织执行董事会加快批准一笔新贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/ethiopia-wins-financing-assurances-key-to-unlock-new-imf-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
